{"word":"Asp","slug":"asp","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Asp</b> A venomous serpent<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=33'>Deu 32:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=20&verse=14'>Job 20:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=20&verse=16'>Job 20:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=11&verse=8'>Isa 11:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=3&verse=13'>Rom 3:13</a><br/> Venom of, illustrates:<br/> - The speech of the wicked<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=140&verse=3'>Psa 140:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=45&chapter=3&verse=13'>Rom 3:13</a> <br/> - Injurious effects of wine<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=32&verse=33'>Deu 32:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=20&chapter=23&verse=32'>Pro 23:32</a> <br/> Deprived of venom, illustrates conversion<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=11&verse=9'>Isa 11:9</a>"}]}